                           net.dv8tion.jda.core.entities.Guild guild)

      • setAdminIdentifier

        private void setAdminIdentifier(java.lang.String msgText)
        Changes the admin identifier to a set string. Admins are people with the role attached. There isn't any error checking here. The instance will just crash if bad input is presented. The rest of the program will continue running. (As written 7/5/2017).
        Parameters:
        msgText - the command text.
